# Environment Variables for Deployment (like Netlify, Vercel, etc.)

# Gemini API Key for AI Itinerary Generation
# 1. Go to https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# 2. Create a new API key
# 3. Add this key in your deployment environment (Netlify -> Site Settings -> Environment Variables)
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# Google Maps API Key
# Used for the maps embed on the Contact page
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=AIzaSyCgz0pMivQXIF_8F0l5ckqSZKQkv4KOS-E

# Firebase Configuration
# Note: Your Firebase config is currently stored in src/firebase-applet-config.json for ease of use,
# which is generally safe for public client-side Firebase apps as security rules protect the database. 
# However, if you want to use env variables for Firebase, you can define them here and update your src/lib/firebase.ts file.
